The Caretaker Extra-Ordinary Convention Planning Committee (CECPC) of the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) has rolled out time table for the conduct of party’s congresses from the ward to zonal levels. The time table is however silent on the National Convention of the party. Secretary to the Committee, Senator John James Akpanduoehehe, disclosed these to newsmen at the party secretariat in Abuja after their meeting under Gov. Mai Mala Buni. The party secretary directed the party’s Director of Organisation, Prof. Ussiju Medear to release the details of the time table/schedule of the congresses. Details shortly…